  <brief_title>A Safety And Efficacy Study Of The Combination Of Oral PF-00299804 And Intravenous CP-751,871 Given Every 3 Weeks</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase 1 Targeted Combination Trial Of PF-00299804 And CP-751,871 In Patients With Advanced Solid Tumors</official_title>
  <sponsors>
