  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will explore the combination of the oral drug PF-00299804 and intravenous
      CP-751,871 in patients with advanced solid tumor. Each of these drugs have been given
      separately to patients in prior studies, and this study is to establish the safety and
      efficacy of the combination.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
